              BJOO: I matched the elements in the QUDA arrays but one of these
              BJOO: must be ignored (probably the first one?). since in a 
              3 level BJOO:  mg only has 2 coarse solves -->

              <CoarseResidual>0.1 0.1 0.1</CoarseResidual>

              <!-- BJOO: Max iterations
              and relaxation factors  for the coarse solves with same 
              caveat as for the residuals -->

              <MaxCoarseIterations>12 12 8</MaxCoarseIterations>
              <RelaxationOmegaMG>1.0 1.0 1.0</RelaxationOmegaMG>

             
